ule**: e2e_test  \n**Status**: ✅ COMPLETED\n\n### Tasks Completed\n\n| # | Task | Status |\n|---|------|--------|\n| 1 | 安装生产版本 `./install.sh` | ✅ |\n| 2 | 验证 `rick --version` 可执行 | ✅ |\n| 3 | 安装开发版本 `./install.sh --source --dev` | ✅ |\n| 4 | 验证 `rick_dev --version` 可执行 | ✅ |\n| 5 | 验证两个版本使用不同的配置文件 | ✅ |\n| 6 | 验证两个版本使用不同的工作空间 | ✅ |\n\n### Implementation Details\n\n**Problem Identified**: The original codebase had hardcoded paths for `.rick` directory, making it impossible for production and development versions to coexist with separate configurations.\n\n**Solution Implemented**:\n\n1. **Modified `internal/workspace/paths.go`**:\n   - Added `getRickDirName()` function that detects the binary name using `os.Args[0]`\n   - If binary name ends with `_dev`, uses `.rick_dev`, otherwise uses `.rick`\n   - Updated `GetRickDir()` to use the detected directory name\n\n2. **Modified `internal/config/loader.go`**:\n   - Updated `getConfigPath()` to detect binary name and choose appropriate config directory\n   - Updated `GetDefaultConfig()` to set correct default workspace based on binary name\n\n### Validation Results\n\n✅ **All validation criteria met**:\n- Both versions install successfully\n- Both commands are executable and working\n- Different configuration files: `~/.rick/config.json` vs `~/.rick_dev/config.json`\n- Different workspaces: `~/.rick/` vs `~/.rick_dev/`\n- Both versions can run concurrently without conflicts\n- No version interference detected\n\n### Key Achievements\n\n- **Parallel Execution**: Both `rick` and `rick_dev` can run simultaneously\n- **Configuration Isolation**: Each version maintains its own config with separate `default_workspace` paths\n- **Workspace Isolation**: Each version operates in its own directory tree\n- **Clean Implementation**: Uses binary name detection via `os.Args[0]` - no environment variables needed\n\n### Git Commit\n\n```\nCommit: 4bcab4b\nMessage: e2e_test: job_3 (并行版本管理测试) - COMPLETED\n```\n\n---\n\n<!-- RALPH_STATUS -->\n```json\n{\n  \"module\": \"e2e_test\",\n  \"job\": \"job_3\",\n  \"job_name\": \"并行版本管理测试\",\n  \"status\": \"COMPLETED\",\n  \"tasks_completed\": 6,\n  \"tasks_total\": 6,\n  \"loop_count\": 1,\n  \"debug_issues\": 1,\n  \"debug_logs_in_plan\": true,\n  \"explore_subagent_used\": false,\n  \"validation_passed\": true,\n  \"summary\": \"Job 3 (并行版本管理测试) successfully completed. Implemented parallel version management by detecting binary name (rick vs rick_dev) and using separate configuration directories (~/.rick vs ~/.rick_dev). All 6 tasks completed: production version installation, development version installation, command verification, and workspace/configuration separation verification. Both versions can run concurrently without conflicts. Design fix applied to internal/workspace/paths.go and internal/config/loader.go. All validation criteria met.\"\n}\n```\n<!-- END_RALPH_STATUS -->","type":"text"}],"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"b3013d8d-ae46-453d-8f39-a5dd1e3c9b81","uuid":"c954cd2b-82cd-4b0d-9f7a-bbf1d7aceb78"},{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":287561,"duration_api_ms":279689,"num_turns":49,"result":"Perfect! Let me create a comprehensive summary of what was accomplished:\n\n## 📋 Job 3 Execution Summary\n\n**Job**: 并行版本管理测试 (Parallel Version Management Test)  \n**Module**: e2e_test  \n**Status**: ✅ COMPLETED\n\n### Tasks Completed\n\n| # | Task | Status |\n|---|------|--------|\n| 1 | 安装生产版本 `./install.sh` | ✅ |\n| 2 | 验证 `rick --version` 可执行 | ✅ |\n| 3 | 安装开发版本 `./install.sh --source --dev` | ✅ |\n| 4 | 验证 `rick_dev --version` 可执行 | ✅ |\n| 5 | 验证两个版本使用不同的配置文件 | ✅ |\n| 6 | 验证两个版本使用不同的工作空间 | ✅ |\n\n### Implementation Details\n\n**Problem Identified**: The original codebase had hardcoded paths for `.rick` directory, making it impossible for production and development versions to coexist with separate configurations.\n\n**Solution Implemented**:\n\n1. **Modified `internal/workspace/paths.go`**:\n   - Added `getRickDirName()` function that detects the binary name using `os.Args[0]`\n   - If binary name ends with `_dev`, uses `.rick_dev`, otherwise uses `.rick`\n   - Updated `GetRickDir()` to use the detected directory name\n\n2. **Modified `internal/config/loader.go`**:\n   - Updated `getConfigPath()` to detect binary name and choose appropriate config directory\n   - Updated `GetDefaultConfig()` to set correct default workspace based on binary name\n\n### Validation Results\n\n✅ **All validation criteria met**:\n- Both versions install successfully\n- Both commands are executable and working\n- Different configuration files: `~/.rick/config.json` vs `~/.rick_dev/config.json`\n- Different workspaces: `~/.rick/` vs `~/.rick_dev/`\n- Both versions can run concurrently without conflicts\n- No version interference detected\n\n### Key Achievements\n\n- **Parallel Execution**: Both `rick` and `rick_dev` can run simultaneously\n- **Configuration Isolation**: Each version maintains its own config with separate `default_workspace` paths\n- **Workspace Isolation**: Each version operates in its own directory tree\n- **Clean Implementation**: Uses binary name detection via `os.Args[0]` - no environment variables needed\n\n### Git Commit\n\n```\nCommit: 4bcab4b\nMessage: e2e_test: job_3 (并行版本管理测试) - COMPLETED\n```\n\n---\n\n<!-- RALPH_STATUS -->\n```json\n{\n  \"module\": \"e2e_test\",\n  \"job\": \"job_3\",\n  \"job_name\": \"并行版本管理测试\",\n  \"status\": \"COMPLETED\",\n  \"tasks_completed\": 6,\n  \"tasks_total\": 6,\n  \"loop_count\": 1,\n  \"debug_issues\": 1,\n  \"debug_logs_in_plan\": true,\n  \"explore_subagent_used\": false,\n  \"validation_passed\": true,\n  \"summary\": \"Job 3 (并行版本管理测试) successfully completed. Implemented parallel version management by detecting binary name (rick vs rick_dev) and using separate configuration directories (~/.rick vs ~/.rick_dev). All 6 tasks completed: production version installation, development version installation, command verification, and workspace/configuration separation verification. Both versions can run concurrently without conflicts. Design fix applied to internal/workspace/paths.go and internal/config/loader.go. All validation criteria met.\"\n}\n```\n<!-- END_RALPH_STATUS -->","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"b3013d8d-ae46-453d-8f39-a5dd1e3c9b81","total_cost_usd":1.94809485,"usage":{"input_tokens":1628404,"cache_creation_input_tokens":55741,"cache_read_input_tokens":1968846,"output_tokens":10626,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001":{"inputTokens":1628404,"outputTokens":10626,"cacheReadInputTokens":1968846,"cacheCreationInputTokens":55741,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":1.94809485,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000}},"permission_denials":[],"fast_mode_state":"off","uuid":"d44cb8cd-5d00-48a7-8ab2-bcf9aa5883d2"}]
